summary: Play as Alisia Varestad a lvl 21 Nord who is making a living as a noble thief, stealing from the rich and give to the poor is her motto.
descriptionHtml:
As Alisia Varedstad you will play as a noble thief who steals from the rich and give\'s to the poor, she is the secret Guild Master of the Thief\'s Guild, doing her daily job as a Arch-Mage of the Collage of Winterhold she studies to find a way to stop hunger amongst the poor.

So will you lead Alisia to her dream of helping the poor or become anoffer rake who just will be anoffer trouble time.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
If there is any bugs please report them in the comment section.

Just place the Savefile under C:\\Users\\Username\\Documents\\My Games\\Skyrim\\Saves
author: CrazyWolfGamer
